---
description: Enforce Matches-only assertions in test files
globs: src/tests/**/*.ts
alwaysApply: false
---

# Type Tests: Matches Only

- Allowed assertion forms:
    - `Expect<Matches<Actual, Expected>>`
- Disallow:
    - `Expect<...>` where the inner type is not `Matches<...>`
    - direct conditional boolean assertions (`T extends U ? true : false`)
- In `Matches<Actual, Expected>`, keep `Expected` explicit and inline in test files (avoid indirection via helper aliases/index lookups).
